      "role": "user",
      "content": "When you mention a potential \"loss of cohesion and unity,\" are you implying that these demographic shifts represent a fundamental threat to the core values that keep the country stable? Some analysts argue this kind of rapid change is more of a destabilizing force than an evolution. What's your take on that?",
